products.name: DONNA BORN IN ROMA  -Eau De Perfumes- 50 ML
products.descriptionEn: An elegant fragrance featuring a trio of jasmine modernized by vanilla and a woody accord.

products.name: VOCE VIVA -Eau De Perfumes- 50 ML
products.descriptionEn: A floral reinterpretation of Valentino’s contemporary femininity: a heady harmony, a timeless, unexpected and addictive fragrance.

products.name: PARADOXE -Eau De Perfumes- 50 ML
products.descriptionEn: Une Eau de Perfumes fl orale ambrée qui révèle de nouvelles sensations olfactives en explorant les paradoxes d’ingrédients iconiques.

products.name: FAME -Eau De Perfumes- 50 ML
products.descriptionEn: Fame combines an exceptionally pure jasmine with a succulent mango and a creamy, sensual, addictive incense.

products.name: My Way - Eau de Perfumes
products.descriptionEn: Discover My Way, the new feminine fragrance by Giorgio Armani. My Way is an invitation to broaden your horizons and live meaningful encounters around the world. A bright white floral bouquet is encapsulated in a talisman bottle, a metaphor for the world.

products.name: LUNA ROSA OCEAN -Eau De Toilette- 50 ML
products.descriptionEn: A signature encapsulating a burst of bergamot, contrasted with the sensuality of vetiver and iris notes.

products.name: Scandal pour homme EDT 50 ML
products.descriptionEn: With muscled elegance and boxing gloves on, the new Scandal pour homme hits hard with an energising and addictive eau de toilette. A woody oriental fragrance with notes of tonka bean, sage and vetiver. Refillable bottle.

products.name: Montre Retro Multifonction
products.descriptionEn: This multifunction quartz watch (day, date and 24-hour) features classy touches: stainless steel case, black leather strap and dial with detailed finishes. Elegant, it is also practical: the hands glow in the dark and the mineral glass reinforced. Water resistance 5 ATM: shower or swim resistant (surface only).

products.name: Huile Prodigieuse X 2 + GIFT
products.descriptionEn: The all-in-one product that nourishes, repairs,and beautifi es skin and hair from fi rst application. Silicone and paraben free.

products.name: Azzaro - Eau de Toilette
products.descriptionEn: A liverly powerful sillage that combines natural sensuality ans elegance. Notes of anise, lavender and vetiver.

products.name: White watch
products.descriptionEn: The iconic design details of the polo shirt are brought to the wrist with a sleek and modern reinterpretation of the Lacoste.12.12 for her. A petit-piqué pattern on the outer of the bold curved dial and the center of the silicone strap provides eye-catching detail, while a crocodile at 3 o’clock adds signature Lacoste branding. Offered in a choice of monochrome colors, the watch is complete with hands and stick indexes in polished metal for a feminine touch. 2-year international warranty.

products.name: Phantom EDT 50ML
products.descriptionEn: Futuristic aromatic fragrance born from the clash between luxury craftmanship and new tech. A bold scent with notes of addictive creamy lavender, energising lemon and sexy, woody vanilla.

products.name: ARMANI CODE Perfumes -Eau De Perfumes- 75 ML
products.descriptionEn: Fragrance for men with aromatic and woody notes,for a powerful and sensual trail.

products.name: Black watch
products.descriptionEn: Lacoste reinvents the Lacoste.12.12 for a new generation as it reinterprets the brand’s signature watch in a sleek and minimalist design. With a new rounded and faceted case and matt-finish bezel, the three-hand timepiece is offered in a choice of monochrome colors including the classic Lacoste green. Inspired by the iconic polo shirt, the timepiece features a crocodile at 3 o’clock, and a petit piqué pattern at the center of the silicone strap and the outer of the bold curved dial. 2-year international warranty.

products.name: Duo of Leather Bracelets for Men
products.descriptionEn:
Stylish and trendy Lambretta bracelets in braided genuine leather,
one in black and one in cognac brown. Stainless steel clasp in
elegant chrome or with an exclusive gold plating. 2 years
international warranty.

products.name: Sound and Light Toothbrush - IRON MAN
products.descriptionEn:
Become an Avenger and join Iron Man on his mission to develop a
healthy oral care routine! Press the button and the brush will light up
for one minute to time your cleaning! It’s the ultimate Avengers
weapon in the fight against plaque! Includes authentic Iron Man
thrusters sounds and encouraging Tony Stark phrases including
‘official brushing hours are between 7 and 8 every day’ and ‘who’s
not brushing’. The cover doubles up to protect the brush when
travelling. Batteries included.

products.name: Crystaldust Double Bangle Bracelet
products.descriptionEn:
A new signature design to equal Stardust and Slake, the
irresistible Crystaldust Bangle is crafted using Swarovski’s
Crystal Rock technique. It is lavishly encrusted with goldentoned
crystals for unparalleled sparkle. Its on-trend spiral
silhouette is versatile and expressive, whilst the gold PVD metal
capped ends, embellished with crystals, finish its clean design
perfectly. Slip on to your arm for instant glamour or layer with
others for a high-octane look.

products.name: Super Lustrous Lip Cube
products.descriptionEn: An enticing lip wardrobe of 9 best selling shades. Infused with  mega-moisturizers and vitamins for silky smooth, soft and seductive  looking lips.

products.name: Unisex Retro Watch
products.descriptionEn: Professional and sleek, this retro style timepiece is a must-have for your collection. Stylish with a classic presentation this watch boasts a fashionable vintage case and digital dial. The watch compliments the case with a quality bracelet and is powered by a highly accurate quartz movement. Additional features include chronograph alarm, time/date and stopwatch. Two Years International Warranty.

products.name: Set of 12 Emoticone bracelets
products.descriptionEn: Un fantastique set de 12 bracelets Emoticone parfait pour toute la famille ou pour partager entre amis. Cet ensemble exclusif inclue les emojis les plus propulsifs avec deux éditions limitées argentées et dorées. Les bracelets élastiques s’adapteront à tous les poignets et sont présentés dans un petit sac en toile pratique pour les ranger ou garder ses affaires au sec au bord de la piscine !

products.name: Construction set
products.descriptionEn: Build 12 different models from the same parts (one at a time)! The patented snap-fit system will provide hours of fun while also enhancing creativity and imagination. Either download or follow step by step instructions. Free app for Android, Apple iOS and Windows is available to view the models in 3D.

products.name: Fixr 20 in 1 Muti-Tools
products.descriptionEn: Always ready for use, with the most useful array of tools possible. The  revolutionary Multitool comes with amazing 20 tools in 1, but weights  only 40 grams. Clip to anything and simply twist into set positions to use  it to open parcels, envelopes or bottles, set screws, use as a ruler and  much more. Engineered in stainless steel, coated with gold and black titanium. Black calf leather protection cover inclusive.

products.name: Compact Styler detangles Rose Gold
products.descriptionEn:
Both luxury and cool, rose gold is having a serious fashion moment.
Detangle on-the-go with the new Rose Gold LUXE Compact Styler
detangling hairbrush, pink hued and pretty with the creamiest of ivories.
Scooping over 30 awards, this innovative beauty tool works like no
other to detangle hair painlessly and easily. The secret lies in the teeth which flex through hair to gently loosen tangles with no tugging or pulling, leaving hair super shiny and smooth.

products.name: Compact Styler detangles Prism
products.descriptionEn: The Tangle Teezer Compact Styler detangles and styles providing the perfect finishing touch thanks to the unique two-tiered teeth system leaving hair super shiny and smooth. The Compact Styler comes with a detachable, click-on, click-off cover that helps protect the teeth when carrying in a handbag. Scooping over 30 awards, this innovative beauty tool works like no other to detangle hair painlessly and easily.

products.name: ANGEL STAR-Eau de Perfumes- 25 ML + FREE
products.descriptionEn:
a glamourous journey through the angel dream, with the sensual and delicious
notes of Angel Eau de Perfumes: bergamot, praline, patchouli & vanilla

products.name: Amour Air Duo IWALK
products.descriptionEn: Chipset bluetooth 5.0 intégré, assure un signal stable, une transmission plus rapide et une consommation réduite. La batterie au lithium intégrée de 60 mAh offre 3,5 heures d’écoute et le boîtier de charge ortable de 500 mAh permet une autonomie totale de 14 heures de lecture. Ne vous inquiétez jamais de la faible charge de la batterie : la toute dernière technologie de diaphragme vibrant et des basses super équilibrées pour un son naturel en 3D, vous permettent de vous perdre dans la musique.
